						               													<description>Cursed by a witch on Halloween Night, Scream or Die lets you and your friends take on the roles of up to 8 mischievous monsters as they compete for candy to lift the witch's curse.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Scream or Die is a dice game where you control the roll even when you aren't rolling!  Each turn, one player randomly draws dice from a bag and rolls them, but all players can use Screams, the monster's currency, to affect the roll.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;If you don't like the dice, add more. If you don't like the roll, shake it up!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;At the end of the turn, collect your candy, collect your screams and pass the bag of dice to the next monster at the table. Scream or Die is for 2-8 players and last 15-25 minutes.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
